ress of the implementation ab 32 california's greenhouse emissions permit cap and trade program this panel focused on current implementation challenges and trading activity in advance of the market opening html+ read more platts conference details http www platts com conferencedet search news everything news of interest wolak speaks to the western chapter at energy bar association march 2 2012 news pesd director frank wolak answers nuclear power question on freakonomics blog june 27 2011 in the news china's green gift to the world environmentalists who want to ban china's coal imports are 100 wrong driving up the price of coal cuts carbon emissions frank wolak richard k morse guardian co uk on december 30 2010 support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
